df1=pd.DataFrame({
    'date':['2013-11-24','2013-11-24','2013-11-24','2013-11-24'],
    'id':['001','002','003','004'],
    'quantity':[22,8,7,10],
    'color':['Yellow','Orange','Red','Yellow'],
})
df2=pd.DataFrame({
    'date':['2013-11-24','2013-11-25','2013-11-24','2013-11-24'],
    'id':['001','002', '004', '005'],
    'quantity':[22,6,5,10],
    'color':['Yellow','Orange','Red','Pink'],
})
